public static List&lt;int&gt; CheckStock(List&lt;Product&gt; ps) { var query = from s in ps where s.Qty &lt;= 10 select s.Id; var toBeRestock = query.ToList(); return toBeRestock; } Qn2   Advantages  Combined with ORM framework such as EntityFramework, it allows a type-safe encoding of database query C# compiler checks for syntax errors of query C# compiler checks for semantic errors of the query  For example, relational property among models.
